meta_title: W/LOGO RYAN COMPANIES DYNEEMA GLOVE LARGE CUT LEVEL 3
description: Gloves only work if people wear them. These gloves are strong and tough, yet comfortable, cool and lightweight. You will love to wear them! Dyneema gloves naturally mold to your hand making them very comfortable and help reduce injuries. Dyneema is pound for pound, 15 times stronger than steel. Even though these gloves are resistant to many chemicals and ultraviolet light, you can still easily wash them. They are more durable than polyester and 40% stronger than Aramid fibers. Dyneema gloves are generally coated to allow for better grip and abrasion resistance. Majestic's President's Choice Glove. These lightweight Dyneema gloves offer superior cut protection as well as durability, dexterity and comfort.  These Dyneema CUT-LESS glove are 13 gauge, ring spun Dyneema seamless knits. Seamless means there are no seams which make this glove very comfortable.
